sequenceDiagram
    participant Patient
    participant ReadingPage as Reading Page
    participant Validation
    participant DB as Database

    Patient->>ReadingPage: Open "Add Reading"
    Patient->>ReadingPage: Enter reading value
    ReadingPage->>Validation: Validate data
    Validation-->>ReadingPage: OK
    ReadingPage->>DB: Save(newReading)
    DB-->>ReadingPage: Success
    ReadingPage->>Patient: Show "Reading Added Successfully"
